    "Cross-card mode pairs by filename. Verify that files on different cards are truly the same photo (camera filenames can repeat).": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "跨卡模式：按文件名跨卡配对。请确认下方清单中各卡的文件确实对应同一张照片（相机文件名可能重复）。"
